PeriodDeterminationMethodCode.description:
Remark:
Values:
1 - Time Unit;
2 - Calendar Unit;
3 - Contract Lifetime;
4 - Term Agreement Fixing Period;
5 - Calendar Unit with Start Day
Integrity conditions:
In case of 1 or 2 Duration must be provided.
In case of 5 Duration and DurationStartMonth and/or DurationStartDayOfMonth must be provided. DurationStartDayOfMonth in case of calendar month duration.
DurationStartMonth and DurationStartDayOfMonth in case of calendar year duration.
In case of 3 and 4 Duration, DurationStartMonth and DurationStartDayOfMonth must not be provided.
BDT: BankAccountEntryRestrictionPeriodDeterminationMethodCode

